d equally well and the generalized\npower-law rating curve mimicked the power-law rating curve.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Oct 2020 19:11:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Aug 2021 01:40:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-10"}
