 the previous century, consistent with the delayed activation of buried\nsupervolatiles (and/or the crystallization of sub-surface amorphous ice) by\nconducted heat following an inward displacement of the perihelion. A potential\norigin in the debris cloud produced by avalanche is also considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 10 Oct 2020 14:27:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-13"}
