rvive under intense radiation fields than presumed, or that PAH\nemission is shifted to shorter wavelengths in intense and high energy radiation\nenvironments. A photometric surrogate for 3.3 $\\mu m$ PAH luminosity using\nJWST/NIRCam is provided and found to be highly reliable at low redshift.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 10 Oct 2020 15:49:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-23"}
